  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether inhaled corticosteroid (specially
      nebulized) could be a good alternative to oral corticosteroid and whether they are effective
      in the treatment of sinusitis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
